text: Hannan Crystal (born 15 January 1938) is an Israeli former sports shooter. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:Israeli male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Israel Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tel Aviv
